  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Describe the role Schr&#1255;dinger&#8217;s equation plays in quantum mechanics</item>
<item>Explain the difference between time-dependent and -independent Schr&#1255;dinger&#8217;s equations</item>  
<item>Interpret the solutions of Schr&#1255;dinger&#8217;s equation</item>
</list></md:abstract>
